            "text": "Zungur utters a powerful croak that deals 4d6 sonic damage to any non-boggard within a 15-foot emanation. Any creature with the frightened condition takes additional sonic damage equal to twice the value of its frightened condition. Zungur can't use Destructive Croak again for 1d4 rounds.",
