                "type": "stat_block_section"
              }
            ],
            "subtype": "ability",
            "text": "If Zungur hits a creature with their tongue, that creature becomes grabbed by the boggard. Unlike with a normal Grab, the creature is not immobilized, but it can't move beyond the reach of Zungur's tongue. The DC to Escape is 18, or a creature can sever the tongue by hitting AC 15 and dealing at least 4 slashing damage. Though this doesn't deal any damage Zungur, it prevents them from using their tongue Strike again until they regrow their tongue, which takes a week.",
            "type": "stat_block_section"
          },
          "name": "Tongue Grab",
          "offensive_action_type": "ability",
          "subtype": "offensive_action",
          "type": "stat_block_section"
